12:16.944 --> 12:18.070
Or-- Or just, you know...

12:18.904 --> 12:20.156
not mediocre.

12:25.202 --> 12:26.495
Parking lot D.

12:29.457 --> 12:31.667
Yeah, I-- I-- I knew that's where it was.

12:36.088 --> 12:37.840
